title: White House says Biden has agreed to meet with Putin 'in principle' as long as Russia does not invade Ukraine - CNN
content:
1. White House says Biden has agreed to meet with Putin 'in principle' as long as Russia does not invade Ukraine  CNN
  2. President Biden Agrees 'In Principle' to Meet with Putin if Russia Does Not Invade Ukraine  CBS Los Angeles
  3. Russia-Ukraine: Biden briefed by security advisers as Russian commanders receive invasion orders  Fox News
  4. The latest on the Ukraine-Russia border crisis: Live updates  CNN
  5. Biden, Putin Agree 'in Principle' to Summit, White House Says  Bloomberg Politics
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: President Joe Biden has agreed "in principle" to French-brokered summit talks with Russian President Vladimir Putin as long as Russia does not further invade Ukraine, the White House said late Sunday.
